 style="width:188px;height:50px;">\r\n				<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n					<span style="color:#0000cd;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>Đơn gi&aacute; trẻm em </strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n				<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n					<span style="color:#0000cd;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>từ 2 đến dưới 12 tuổi (VNĐ)</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:173px;height:29px;">\r\n				<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n					<span style="color:#0000cd;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>&ge; 20</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:188px;height:29px;">\r\n				<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n					<span style="color:#0000cd;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>43.900.000</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:188px;height:29px;">\r\n				<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n					<span style="color:#0000cd;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>33.520.000</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color:#ff0000;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong><u>GI&Aacute; TR&Ecirc;N BAO GỒM:</u></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- Kh&aacute;ch sạn ti&ecirc;u chuẩn &nbsp;<strong>04 &nbsp;sao</strong> quốc tế, 2 kh&aacute;ch/ph&ograve;ng (trường hợp lẻ người bố tr&iacute; ngủ ph&ograve;ng 3)</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- C&aacute;c bữa ăn theo chương tr&igrave;nh</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- Phương tiện vận chuyển: &Ocirc; t&ocirc; điều ho&agrave; đời mới</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- V&eacute; m&aacute;y bay khứ hồi Việt Nam &ndash; Ch&acirc;u &Acirc;u:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>TK 168 L&nbsp; TU&nbsp; HANIST HK20&nbsp; 2125 0405*</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; TK1821 L&nbsp; WE&nbsp; ISTCDG HK20&nbsp; 0650 0930</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; TK1954 L&nbsp; SU&nbsp; AMSIST HK20&nbsp; 1935 0010*</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; TK 166 L&nbsp; MO&nbsp; ISTHAN HK20&nbsp; 0220 1520</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- Lệ ph&iacute; s&acirc;n bay + phụ ph&iacute; xăng dầu</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- Ph&iacute; dịch thuật, c&ocirc;ng chứng c&aacute;c t&agrave;i liệu tr&igrave;nh ĐSQ xin cấp Visa</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- Visa nhập cảnh Ch&acirc;u &Acirc;u</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- HDV suốt tuyến cho đo&agrave;n tr&ecirc;n 12 kh&aacute;ch &ndash; HDV bản địa cho đo&agrave;n dưới 12 &nbsp;kh&aacute;ch</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- Bảo hiểm du lịch suốt tuyến: 30.000 EURO</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- V&eacute; thắng cảnh (cửa 1) tại c&aacute;c điểm du lịch</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- Qu&agrave; tặng: vỏ hộ chiếu, mũ du lịch, ba lo du lịch, gối chữ U</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="color:#ff0000;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;"><strong><u>GI&Aacute; TR&Ecirc;N KH&Ocirc;NG BAO GỒM:</u></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- Ph&iacute; hộ chiếu, chi ti&ecirc;u c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, h&agrave;nh l&yacute; qu&aacute; cước</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- Đồ uống, chi ph&iacute; điện thoại, giặt l&agrave; trong kh&aacute;ch sạn</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- Phụ ph&iacute; sử dụng ph&ograve;ng đơn</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif;">- Phụ thu đối với kh&aacute;ch nước ngo&agrave;i đi